Scream Queens, Empire

00:10.845 --> 00:12.378
<i>and</i> Grandfathered.

00:12.380 --> 00:14.380
This is Edie,
your granddaughter.

00:14.382 --> 00:15.748
<i>Only on Fox.</i>

